itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:17:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>配藥員依啲下欄位  ... 隨時被取代  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西藥配藥其實讀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好奇想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.vtc.edu.hk/admission/tc/programme/as124203-higher-diploma-in-dispensing-studies/curriculum/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vtc.edu.hk%2Fadmission%2Ftc%2Fprogramme%2Fas124203-higher-diploma-in-dispensing-studies%2Fcurriculum%2F&d=CpdBlFin1w%2F29JcLDvXN%2BywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=13395997\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vtc.edu.hk/admission/tc/programme/as124203-higher-diploma-in-dispensing-studies/curriculum/</a><br />\n<br />\n又化學 theory ,  之後記下藥名藥性病理咁呱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n依家死位嚟架 ... 又唔會畀人當你專業  但又要讀啲好專既野 <br />\n<br />\n更弊既係  職場飽和"},{"pid":"fac57438e9e803c026333f907b6460383931ebd5","tid":291853,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:19:08.000Z","msg":"唔該曬咁多巴打意見"},{"pid":"5e14a0cf9a0b237d6f50b9137e5e8205e40596a4","tid":291853,"uid":59906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:25:27.000Z","msg":"有同行喎<br />\n垃圾 中藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50d904ce074b35f893ef882344a5354fd8ca8cb","tid":291853,"uid":51260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:05:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"167a9dc7c93a730b2fe57f53613133b89383dc7f","tid":291853,"uid":51260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:06:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab4e1942f14bf36fdd77e505cebb49ed74d3927e","tid":291853,"uid":68377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:18:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有工開先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSupply大過demand?</blockquote><br />\n全行pharm + dispenser 幾百人失業呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢家已經有啲pharm撚做住dispenser先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw pharm呢科真係比hku累死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本來cu一間開已經好夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收咁高分出來搵唔到工咁慘?</blockquote><br />\n記得好似工會都屌哂鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係總之有唔少人數都做唔番長工(見ha通常都係請pt/temp.contract)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲可能做住街房,私家診所,藥廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fde3fe3deac1c96dcf3519c9542b1ce32df5078","tid":291853,"uid":51260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:20:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5a4aa254d4121b117ca3c2844652a4f84fd3b8b","tid":291853,"uid":68377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:24:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>配藥員依啲下欄位  ... 隨時被取代  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西藥配藥其實讀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好奇想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.vtc.edu.hk/admission/tc/programme/as124203-higher-diploma-in-dispensing-studies/curriculum/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vtc.edu.hk%2Fadmission%2Ftc%2Fprogramme%2Fas124203-higher-diploma-in-dispensing-studies%2Fcurriculum%2F&d=CpdBlFin1w%2F29JcLDvXN%2BywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=13395997\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vtc.edu.hk/admission/tc/programme/as124203-higher-diploma-in-dispensing-studies/curriculum/</a><br />\n<br />\n又化學 theory ,  之後記下藥名藥性病理咁呱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n依家死位嚟架 ... 又唔會畀人當你專業  但又要讀啲好專既野 <br />\n<br />\n更弊既係  職場飽和</blockquote><br />\n真係好專業咁</blockquote><br />\n其實主要係熟藥理,要清楚啲藥用途(醫咩病),副作用,drug class,allergy,有啲用具例如insulin pen,inhalers等等你要認識點用再教病人<br />\n但係通常用開既藥大約有500隻到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c99ecb2cdcf75a3af556ad5b1d482e669ede10","tid":291853,"uid":68377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:24:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有工開先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSupply大過demand?</blockquote><br />\n全行pharm + dispenser 幾百人失業呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢家已經有啲pharm撚做住dispenser先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw pharm呢科真係比hku累死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本來cu一間開已經好夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收咁高分出來搵唔到工咁慘?</blockquote><br />\n記得好似工會都屌哂鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係總之有唔少人數都做唔番長工(見ha通常都係請pt/temp.contract)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲可能做住街房,私家診所,藥廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n私家診所只請女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsor我指卓健,明心個啲集團診所<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3253cc8bcc218fb261608a828e0cc58c70187d1a","tid":291853,"uid":68377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:25:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>配藥員依啲下欄位  ... 隨時被取代  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n長遠其實都唔係幾想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec20133b5fbdca6a7a652999edb5232293364583","tid":291853,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:27:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>配藥員依啲下欄位  ... 隨時被取代  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n長遠其實都唔係幾想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔明點解仲未有配藥自動化糸統   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇配藥員 / 藥劑師 答下我 ?"},{"pid":"e5e8962ecd791f1bf3ecff7e9dc4bf5304c3937c","tid":291853,"uid":59906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:39:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有同行喎<br />\n垃圾 中藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你Ive 定太空</blockquote><br />\nive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ac3152807d18d51c2dbfdecb53abbf98792ca6","tid":291853,"uid":59906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:43:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>配藥員依啲下欄位  ... 隨時被取代  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n長遠其實都唔係幾想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔明點解仲未有配藥自動化糸統   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇配藥員 / 藥劑師 答下我 ?</blockquote><br />\n成本問題掛<br />\n請一個人唔係好貴<br />\n你要諗下將一樣工作自動化<br />\n需要一定既金錢<br />\n如果回唔到本就不如繼續用人<br />\n所以未來ai首先取代既係高人工既工種<br />\nsor 少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b035b9120dfcb8d536b882087e4dee6f1eb63f46","tid":291853,"uid":51260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:52:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa86cd9a076bff31a1a556ccc1a9f6d9166d48b8","tid":291853,"uid":51260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:53:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e77e10c0adda46512dae308d633a60f313a4d2f","tid":291853,"uid":59906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:02:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有同行喎<br />\n垃圾 中藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你Ive 定太空</blockquote><br />\nive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIve個邊d人畢業之後會番大陸讀中醫？</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n會 有fd上去讀<br />\n我覺得投資太大同風險太高<br />\n唔計學順生活費 要用6年時間去讀<br />\n返到黎未必考到牌<br />\n考唔到牌就真係食屎都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991bf337dea3d7d5bd6f4a4b310cb2322ccf65ca","tid":291853,"uid":51260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:04:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06054615804240c971173c6fcbf90fca694b630f","tid":291853,"uid":51260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:06:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e7a6e0344c53585bc1b41da94bb1ca9344d480c","tid":291853,"uid":59906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:19:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有同行喎<br />\n垃圾 中藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你Ive 定太空</blockquote><br />\nive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIve個邊d人畢業之後會番大陸讀中醫？</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n會 有fd上去讀<br />\n我覺得投資太大同風險太高<br />\n唔計學順生活費 要用6年時間去讀<br />\n返到黎未必考到牌<br />\n考唔到牌就真係食屎都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五年姐 個到有醫院實習 係香港讀先六年</blockquote><br />\n但做執藥一世都得10幾k 人工，女就冇所謂，男就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我個邊好多人都讀完上大陸，仲有個hd 課程編排似學中醫野咁<br />\n<br />\nBtw,巴打畢業左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n畢左三年啦<br />\n係讀5年但係大陸畢業時間比香港遲<br />\n畢完都要等一年先有得考<br />\n唔好以為個試好易<br />\n宜家浸大班友諗住限死大陸生合格率"},{"pid":"799468b550a0e183d739ef443308437c4e8baec1","tid":291853,"uid":51260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:21:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24f231389969a0225c4a98f84e9f78cee99281dd","tid":291853,"uid":59906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:25:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIve個邊d人畢業之後會番大陸讀中醫？</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n會 有fd上去讀<br />\n我覺得投資太大同風險太高<br />\n唔計學順生活費 要用6年時間去讀<br />\n返到黎未必考到牌<br />\n考唔到牌就真係食屎都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五年姐 個到有醫院實習 係香港讀先六年</blockquote><br />\n但做執藥一世都得10幾k 人工，女就冇所謂，男就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我個邊好多人都讀完上大陸，仲有個hd 課程編排似學中醫野咁<br />\n<br />\nBtw,巴打畢業左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n畢左三年啦<br />\n係讀5年但係大陸畢業時間比香港遲<br />\n畢完都要等一年先有得考<br />\n唔好以為個試好易<br />\n宜家浸大班友諗住限死大陸生合格率</blockquote><br />\n但我唔想執藥一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打做過邊間，宜家幾錢人工</blockquote><br />\n做緊三方合作個d邊間唔講啦<br />\n得18間呢行好細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n萬頭 冇辦法啦初時轉工咩都唔識<br />\n不過呢邊有樣好就係d人走得快<br />\n有機會升職<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e1ed639fc3953b552ec294da3f4205640c2db7","tid":291853,"uid":51260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:40:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85ac00f4271f62c8395babac5f487dc18dbf56b4","tid":291853,"uid":68377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T17:05:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>配藥員依啲下欄位  ... 隨時被取代  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n長遠其實都唔係幾想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔明點解仲未有配藥自動化糸統   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇配藥員 / 藥劑師 答下我 ?</blockquote><br />\n新加坡有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以ha咁官僚格同埋法例問題我相信都幾難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}